    schema1:description "\"Polypolish is a tool for polishing genome assemblies with short reads.Polypolish uses SAM files where each read has been aligned to all possible locations (not just a single best location).This allows it to repair errors in repeat regions that other alignment-based polishers cannot fix.\"" ;
